en-US.title: Springs Medical
en-US.description: Springs Medical is a healthcare provider, offering a broad range of medical services with a commitment towards an environment free of discrimination. It provides a list of special clinics such as cervical screening, immunisation, diabetes, and wellness programs. The medical center also commits to boosting better health outcomes for the First Nations peoples - the Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander communities. Springs Medical understands the importance of offering tailored healthcare services to the transgender community to enhance respect and self-determination.
